@startuml IS443 FlagPlaceholderWidget - UI Only Change
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

title IS443 — FlagPlaceholderWidget: UI-only refactoring (no TEA changes)

note as N1
**IS443 — Контракт TEA не затрагивается**

Задача: перенос FlagPlaceholderWidget
из modules/screen/dictionary в modules/core/ui
и подстановка в 3 точках отображения.

**State:** без изменений
**UI Messages:** без изменений
**Effects:** без изменений
**Datasource Messages:** без изменений
**Reducer:** без изменений

Все изменения — уровень Composable (UI rendering).
end note

package "modules/core/ui" as CoreUI {
  [FlagPlaceholderWidget] as FPW
  note right of FPW
    Перенесён из screen/dictionary
    Package: me.apomazkin.ui
    Default size: 24dp (было 48dp)
    Params: letter, modifier
  end note
}

package "modules/widget/dictionarypicker" as WidgetPicker {
  [DictDropDownWidget] as DDW
  [ItemDictMenuWidget] as IDMW
}

package "modules/screen/dictionary" as ScreenDict {
  [DictionaryListItemWidget] as DLIW
  [DictionaryFormWidget] as DFW
}

DDW --> FPW : if flagRes == 0\nshow placeholder\n(letter = currentDict.title.first)
IDMW --> FPW : if iconRes == 0\nshow placeholder\n(letter = title.first)
DLIW --> FPW : if flagRes == null\nshow placeholder\n(letter = item.name.first)
DFW --> FPW : import change only\nme.apomazkin.ui.*

@enduml
